title: Metatrader Expert Adviser FxExtractor V1.2.0.0
description:
FxExtractor is a sophisticated Metatrader 4 Expert Adviser (EA) for trading the foreign exchange market.

Robustly coded to be unaffected by most network and brokers server errors.

Positions are fully recovered in the event of a computer or program crash.

Generates an average minimum return of 3% per month, typically 6% to 10%.

Relatively low risk, depending on the risk settings in use.

Uses an economic calendar to restrict grid trading around news release times and to trade news releases if the actual deviation is sufficiently different to the forecast value.

Multiple chart trading, even if limited to trading one symbol at a time.
